New scoring script ideas:
-------------------------

- Most recent allruners, most recent ziggurat:27 visits.

General thoughts:
 - all_players: List of all players (alphabetic) with:
    - games (won), best XL, best sc, av score, first game, most recent game
    
 - players_best_score: List of players (best score)
 - per player page:
     - Ten best games.
     - Ten most recent games.
     Break up of:
     - Highest CL.
     - Escapes with orb.
     - Games played
     Break up by race and class.

